Name:           nicify-lib
Version:        1.0.1
Synopsis:       Pretty print the standard output of default `Show` instances.
Description:    Pretty print the standard output of `show` for algebraic datatypes
                
License:        MIT
License-File:   LICENSE
Author:         Julian Fleischer
Maintainer:     julian@scravy.de
Build-Type:     Simple
Cabal-Version:  >= 1.10
Category:       Text, Tools, Utilities
Stability:      stable

Source-Repository head
    type: git
    location: https://github.com/scravy/nicify-lib

Library
    Exposed-Modules:    Text.Nicify
    Build-Depends:      base ==4.*
                        , parsec ==3.*
                        , transformers >= 0.3
    Hs-Source-Dirs:     src
    Default-Language:   Haskell2010
